data.description: Embrace the promise of a NEW beginning in 2024 with this exquisite home nestled in the heart of Islandwalk at the West Villages, just moments from vibrant Downtown Wellen Park! Experience the joy of stepping into a new chapter of your life as you walk through the doors of this LIKE-NEW 2022 sales center turned captivating property. And guess what? We've got incredible news for you – a generous price drop that makes this dream home an absolute steal!    As the New Year unfolds, envision yourself in this stunning 2,589 square foot, 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom, 2-car TANDEM GARAGE with bonus storage home – a space waiting for your unique style to breathe life into it. Situated on a unique and private pie-shaped lot at the end of a tranquil cul-de-sac, this home offers a sense of peace and privacy that’s unparalleled. Rear preserve views with a distant pond teeming with wildlife and no residences across the street adds an extra layer of exclusivity to your slice of paradise.     Imagine waking up to the crisp dawn of a new day in your spacious master bedroom, a sanctuary designed for tranquility with it’s private spa retreat and a walk-in closet that will take your breath away. The airy ambiance and abundant natural light create the perfect canvas for your dreams and aspirations. Did we mention that the home has HURRICANE IMPACT WINDOWS & DOORS throughout? Including the 4-door POCKETING SLIDER leading to an over-sized lanai!     The heart of this home, the kitchen, beckons culinary adventures and hearty gatherings. BRAND NEW appliances, REVERSE OSMOSIS SYSTEM, WATER SOFTENER, QUARTZ COUNTERTOPS, and ample counter space offer the ideal setup to craft delectable meals for loved ones while planning the year ahead.    Step outside and discover your own private oasis – a backyard offering endless opportunities for relaxation and entertainment. Want to add a pool? NO PROBLEM! This lot has plenty of depth for your creative and custom designs!     This stunning residence is nestled in a thriving community that offers an impressive array of amenities. From 8 har-tru tennis courts, lap pools, resort pools, and relaxing spas to 6 bocce courts for friendly games and social gatherings, a complete fitness center, movement room, community library, arts and crafts room, catering kitchen, BBQ grills, and an Event Center building - this place has it all!    The brand-new Clubhouse campus takes luxury living to the next level. Picture serene lap pools, a resort pool, and a relaxing spa alongside card rooms, a state-of-the-art fitness center, a movement room, and a cozy fire pit for relaxed evenings with neighbors and friends.    Enjoy 12 dedicated pickleball courts, a community garden, a tot lot, a dog park, and a half-court for basketball enthusiasts - offering a lifestyle that balances recreation and relaxation seamlessly.    Beyond the captivating features of this home, the location is the cherry on top. Within a 15-minute drive, bask in the sandy beaches of the Gulf Coast. Explore the vibrant local scene of Downtown Wellen Park, easily accessible via your golf cart. Sports enthusiasts will appreciate the close proximity to the Atlanta Braves Spring Training Facility at CoolToday Park.     And here's the cherry on top – an irresistible price decrease! The perfect opportunity to make this your own without breaking the bank. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to start afresh in a place that resonates with your aspirations and dreams. Contact us today!
